    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/6f133b09bb44f59d029a0138f62b0c2f.poster.avif?t=1771688423\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/6f133b09bb44f59d029a0138f62b0c2f.webm?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/6f133b09bb44f59d029a0138f62b0c2f.mp4?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提升厨师技能，解锁甜点食谱</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将帮助柴犬从厨房新手变成经验丰富的大厨。随着经验值的增长，柴犬能够解锁更多奶奶的甜点食谱，各种可爱的柴犬造型甜点不仅满足顾客的味蕾与视觉，还温暖他们的心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/1266e8333f1686d9bc024a6b86795b91.poster.avif?t=1771688423\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/1266e8333f1686d9bc024a6b86795b91.webm?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/1266e8333f1686d9bc024a6b86795b91.mp4?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开店前忙碌备料，享受制作甜点的过程</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揉糯米粉成团，放入沸水中煮至浮起，捞出晾凉，淋上特制的砂糖酱油酱汁……噔噔！香气四溢的柴犬团子闪亮出炉。今天还想用毛茸茸的小手做些什么可爱的甜点来卖呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/d32c67b74a5bbeb0a53b11936165368a.poster.avif?t=1771688423\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/d32c67b74a5bbeb0a53b11936165368a.webm?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/d32c67b74a5bbeb0a53b11936165368a.mp4?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>争分夺秒！开店出售客制化盒装甜点给顾客</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各式各样的顾客排成长队，只为品尝您亲手制作的美味柴犬甜点！在有限的时间内，将正确的订单打包出售，看到顾客们开心的脸庞，就是最大的动力和幸福。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/7b6cff9cf0732e72779f92a488d8a70f.poster.avif?t=1771688423\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/7b6cff9cf0732e72779f92a488d8a70f.webm?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/7b6cff9cf0732e72779f92a488d8a70f.mp4?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用辛苦赚来的钱装饰厨房和店铺 </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是在现实中还是游戏里，钱都是很重要的！玩家需要用钱购买食材、厨房工具、装饰品，甚至为柴犬买一件可爱的围裙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/5996173c1865135acd5a9556dbd9a36d.poster.avif?t=1771688423\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/5996173c1865135acd5a9556dbd9a36d.webm?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015360/extras/5996173c1865135acd5a9556dbd9a36d.mp4?t=1771688423\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奶奶超级爱你哦！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一个热爱旅行的奶奶是什么样的体验呢？奶奶永远记得她的爱孙，她会在旅行中寄明信片给玩家，那些有趣又搞笑的明信片将成为我们珍贵的收藏品。只能说，奶奶的爱是无敌的！</p>",
